

Animations and Transitions

Adds motion to elements.

/* Transition */
button {
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
}
button:hover {
    background-color: orange;
}

/* Animation */
@keyframes slideIn {
    from {
        transform: translateX(-100%);
    }
    to {
        transform: translateX(0);
    }
}
.animated {
    animation: slideIn 1s ease-in-out;
}
